## Third-Party Libraries and Resources

This plugin may include or be inspired by third-party libraries and resources. 
Below are the acknowledgments and licenses for these components:

### Inspiration
- **jquery-halloween-bats**: The flying bats animation is inspired by the 
  jquery-halloween-bats project by Artimon (https://github.com/Artimon/jquery-halloween-bats)
  
### Emoji Characters
- This plugin uses emoji characters (🦇, 👻, 🎃, 🍂, 🕷️, etc.) which are part of the 
  Unicode standard and are freely available for use.

### Sound Effects (if included)
- Sound effects, if included, may be sourced from various free and open-source 
  libraries. Each sound file should be checked for its individual license terms.
  Common sources include:
  - Freesound.org (Creative Commons licenses)
  - YouTube Audio Library (No attribution required)
  - Zapsplat.com (with appropriate licensing)

### WordPress Framework
- This plugin is built for WordPress and utilizes WordPress APIs and functions
  which are licensed under GPL v2 or later.

